Insider Activity


Individual




Steven F. Leer



Mr. Steven F. Leer is Non-Executive Chairman at USG Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Cenovus Energy, Inc., International Coal Group, Inc., Norfolk Southern Corp., Mineral Information Institute, National Mining Association, The Business Roundtable, The National Coal Council, University of the Pacific, Washington University in St. Louis, Western Business Roundtable and Parsons Corp. Mr. Leer was previously employed as Executive Chairman by Arch Coal, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer by Arch Mineral Corp. He also served on the board at Greater Saint Louis Area Council BSA, National Association of Manufacturers, Natural Resource Partners LP and The Center for Energy & Economic Development. He received his undergraduate degree from Pacific University and an MBA from the University of Washington.



